  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa is offered on a bed and breakfast basis or half board basis which includes breakfast and dinner, drinks not included. </p>
<p>Each morning you can fuel up for the day at the breakfast buffet which has a variety of hot and cold options, as well as eggs cooked to order. A packed breakfast can be provided on request for early departures, you must order early breakfast with reception 24 hours in advance. </p>
<p>After a day of exploring Zermatt, complimentary homemade cake is served between 3-5pm. Drinks are not included.</p>
<p>Each evening you can enjoy a four or five course evening meal with a choice of main course. Throughout the week there is often a themed buffet evening. The menu is prepared with regional produce, and usually consists of traditional dishes with a modern twist.</p>
<p>Marie's Deli restaurant and shop is available in-house, offering local comfort food and traditional dishes throughout the day. This is not included in the half board offering, and is payable locally.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>A Christmas dinner and New Years Eve Gala dinner is included. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
